b.archive.org/web/20110825162711/http://www.breakingnewsonline.net/news/4777-elephant-declared-national-heritage-animal-in-india.html |archivedate=25 August 2011 }}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{IDN}} || [[Komodo dragon]] ''(national animal)''\n||''Varanus komodoensis'' ||[[File:Komododragon2.jpg|150px]] ||<ref>{{Cite book |title=Tourism, conservation, and sustainable development|last=Goodwin |first=Harold J. |author2=Kent, Ivan |author3=Parker, Kim |author4= Walpole, Matt  |year=1998 |publisher=International Institute for Environment and Development |location=London |isbn=978-1-904035-25-1 |page=4 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mfx8CrnbcmUC&pg=PA4#v=onepage&q&f=false |accessdate=25 June 2011 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Garuda Pancasila|Garuda]] ''(historic national animal)''||style=\"background:#ccc;\"|'''Mythical''' ||[[File:National emblem of Indonesia Garuda Pancasila.svg|150px]] ||<ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Lifestyle/national-animals-legendary-extinct-imaginary/story?id=20170452#2 |title=National Animals: The Legendary, Extinct and Imaginary-5 of 9 |publisher=abcnews.go.com |accessdate=2014-10-03}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{IRN}}<!--Iran-->\n|[[Persian lion|Asiatic lion]]\n||''[[Persian lion|Panthera leo persica]]'' || [[File:Asiatic Lion 2 (8682594469).jpg|150x150px]] ||<ref name=\"globalpost.com\">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=esV0hccod0kC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA77#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=Lion and Gazelle: The Mammals and Birds of Iran|last=Humphreys|first=Patrick|date=15 March 1999|website=|publisher=I.B.Tauris, 1999|accessdate=29 October 2016|isbn=9781860642296}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Persian leopard|Persian Leopard]]\n|''Panthera pardus saxicolor''\n|[[File:Persian Leopard sitting.jpg|150x150px]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://animalsake.com/list-of-national-animals-around-world|title=A Complete List of National Animals from Around the World|website=AnimalSake|language=en-US|access-date=2019-09-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.worl