eraldry]]) ||''Bos primigenius indicus'' ||[[File:Z\u00e9bu.JPG|150px]] ||<ref>[https://www.worldatlas.com/webimage/countrys/africa/madagascar/mgsymbols.htm#page Symbols of Madagascar]</ref>\n|-\n| [[Ring-tailed lemur]] ''(national animal)'' ||''Lemur catta'' || [[File:Lemur catta 001.jpg|150px]] ||<ref>[https://www.worldatlas.com/webimage/countrys/africa/madagascar/mgsymbols.htm#page Symbols of Madagascar]</ref>\n|-\n| {{MYS}} || [[Malayan tiger]] ''(national animal)'' ||''Panthera tigris jacksoni'' ||[[File:MalayanTiger.jpg|150px]] ||<ref name=\"DiPiazza2006\">{{cite book|last=DiPiazza|first=Francesca|title=Malaysia in Pictures|url=https://archive.org/details/malaysiainpictur0000dipi|url-access=registration|accessdate=1 January 2012|year=2006|publisher=Twenty-First Century Books|isbn=978-0-8225-2674-2|page=[https://archive.org/details/malaysiainpictur0000dipi/page/14 14]}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{MLT}}\n|[[Pharaoh Hound]] ''(national animal)''\n|''Canis lupus familiaris''\n|[[File:Kelb tal fenek 529.jpg|150px]]\n|[http://dogtime.com/dog-breeds/pharaoh-hound#/slide/1]\n|-\n| {{MDA}} || [[Aurochs]] ''(national animal)'' ||''Bos primigenius'' ||[[File:Aurochs reconstruction.jpg|150px]] ||<ref name=\"Minahan2010\">{{cite book|last=Minahan|first=James|title=The Complete Guide to National Symbols and Emblems: Volume 1 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=jfrWCQAAQBAJ&pg=PA469&lpg=PA469&dq=moldavian+national+animal#v=onepage&q=moldova&f=false|accessdate=2 January 2012|year=2010|publisher=Greenwood Press|isbn=978-0-313-34498-5|page=469}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{MUS}} || [[Dodo]]||''Raphus cucullatus'' ||[[File:Dodo.JPG|150px]] ||<ref name=\"6 Extremely Rare National Animals\"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/science/wildlife-news/130925/interesting-national-animals |title=12 countries that have cooler national animals than the United States |publisher=globalpost.com |accessdate=3 October 2014 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Lifestyle/national-anim