y/gallery%2CWhite-tailed_Eagle_%28Haliaeetus_albicilla%29%2Cgid%2C236008%2Ccid%2C923.htm |title=Polish Birds Directory: White-tailed Eagle (Haliaeetus albicilla) |publisher=birds.poland.pl |accessdate=2016-10-10 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080616044037/http://birds.poland.pl/directory/gallery%2CWhite-tailed_Eagle_%28Haliaeetus_albicilla%29%2Cgid%2C236008%2Ccid%2C923.htm |archivedate=16 June 2008 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://info-poland.buffalo.edu/classroom/eagle.html |title=symbols of Poland: The White Eagle |publisher=buffalo.edu |accessdate=2016-10-10 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010162805/http://info-poland.buffalo.edu/classroom/eagle.html |archivedate=10 October 2016 }}</ref>\n|-\n|[[White stork]] ''(national bird)''||''Ciconia ciconia'' || [[File:Ciconia ciconia - 01.jpg|150px]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thenews.pl/1/9/Artykul/25191,Poland-salutes-the-white-stork|title=Poland salutes the white stork|publisher=thenews.pl|accessdate=2016-10-10|author=}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[European bison]] ''(national animal)''||''Bison bonasus'' ||[[File:European Bison.JPG|150x150px]]||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/travel/2011/apr/09/poland-wildlifeholidays|title=Primeval Poland: where the bison roam|publisher=theguardian.com|accessdate=2016-10-10|author=Jon Eldridge}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://allaboutbison.com/bison-world-news/europe/poland/|title=Poland|publisher=allaboutbison.com|accessdate=2016-10-10|author=}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | {{POR}} || [[Rooster of Barcelos]] ||style=\"background:#ccc;\"|'''Mythical''' || [[File:PA2900302 galo emiliarocha medio.jpg|sans_cadre|150px]]||<ref name=Po1>{{cite web|url=https://www.reference.com/geography/national-animal-portugal-a2c63c3800b560c2|website=www.reference.com|title=What is the national animal of Portugal?|access-date=22 October 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181214061538/https://www.reference.com/geography/nati